.TH "drm_modeset_acquire_init" 9 "drm_modeset_acquire_init" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
drm_modeset_acquire_init \- initialize acquire context
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" drm_modeset_acquire_init
.BI "(struct drm_modeset_acquire_ctx *ctx "  ","
.BI "uint32_t flags "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ctx" 12
the acquire context
.IP "flags" 12
0 or DRM_MODESET_ACQUIRE_INTERRUPTIBLE
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
When passing DRM_MODESET_ACQUIRE_INTERRUPTIBLE to \fIflags\fP,
all calls to \fBdrm_modeset_lock\fP will perform an interruptible
wait.
